                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>During the course of its Eleventh Session at Paris, April 23–26, 1953, the North
                    Atlantic Council adopted a resolution stressing the “paramount importance” which
                    the Atlantic Community continued to attach to the rapid establishment of a
                    European Defense Community. The text of this resolution is printed in the
                    Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, May 11, 1953, pages
                    674–675. For documentation on the Eleventh Session of the North Atlantic
                    Council, see <ref target="#pg_368">pages 368</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
